aitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>经过两个赛季和世界各地的其他几个版本，<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><em>叛徒</em></a>仍然是电视上最受关注的真人秀之一。</p><p>由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼（Claudia Winkleman）主持，第三季看到25名参赛者在苏格兰高地的一座城堡中争夺价值高达12万英镑的奖金。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/best-tv-shows-2025-stranger-things-bear-andor-wednesday-3826471">20个大型电视节目在2025年期待</a></strong></li></ul><p>在城堡中，选出几名参赛者是“叛徒”，他们必须掩盖自己的身份并消除“忠实者”以要求获得奖项。但是，如果忠实的人设法通过每日圆桌会议驱逐所有叛徒，那么所有幸存的参赛者都将赢得现金奖。</p><p>英国广播公司（BBC）去年将演出续签了第四季，还播放了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-uk-celebrity-edition-announced-3786092">九集名人版</a>。</p><h2>谁在第一周离开了<em>叛徒</em>第3季？</h2><p>开幕剧集介绍了所有25名参赛者，尽管他们甚至在踏入城堡之前就进行了火车车辆的转折。三名参赛者不得不提名自己离开火车，不知道结果会是什么。</p><p>选择离开火车的参赛者是亚历山大·德拉格蒂（Alexander Dragonetti），福齐·法西尔（Fozia Fasil）和杰克·马林纳·布朗（Jack Marriner-Brown），他们都被暂时从比赛中撤离。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：尹吕（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg" alt="叛乱者在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827330" class="wp-caption-text"> YinLü在“叛徒”中：BBC和Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>由于叛徒受到了传播博士的怀疑和智力的威胁，尹吕是第三季中第一位被谋杀的参赛者。</p><p><strong>放逐：内森·希德（Nathan Khider）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg" alt="内森在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827328" class="wp-caption-text">内森（Nathan）在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在圆桌会议上对叛徒琳达感到怀疑，但八名球员投票赞成驱逐39年历史的房地产顾问内森（Nathan）。该决定基于他安静的举止之外的证据很少。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：基思·斯图尔特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg" alt="基思在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827333" class="wp-caption-text">基思在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>窗户清洁工基思（Keith）被认为是一个坚强而讨人喜欢的角色，成为叛徒谋杀的第二个人。</p><p><strong>放逐：Elen Wyn（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg" alt="叛徒的埃伦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827334" class="wp-caption-text">埃伦（Elen</figcaption></figure><p>在被其他球员挂钩后，加上她相信大多数叛徒将是“坚强的女性”之后，翻译者埃伦（Elen）被淘汰了。</p><p>她告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crrw4d1lxygo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>：“一旦您的名字出现在那里，就很难拯救自己。”</p><p><strong>放逐：Armani Gouveia（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg" alt="叛徒阿玛尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827329" class="wp-caption-text">阿玛尼（Armani）是第三季中第一个离开的叛徒：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>球员们在第三集中设法消除了他们的第一个叛徒，因为阿玛尼的勇气和指挥态度迅速与她作战。她自己的姐姐迈亚·古维亚（Maia Gouveia）承认对自己的行为有怀疑，她的命运被封锁了。</p><h2>谁在第二周离开？</h2><p>在情节的第二周开始时，以前淘汰了选手亚历山大·龙妮蒂，福齐亚·法西尔和杰克·马里纳·布朗，被带回了一个挑战，使他们挂在森林中的笼子里。</p><p>玩家只能节省三名悬而未决的参赛者中的两名，然后从这一点开始就加入了比赛。在提出了令人信服的争论之后，亚历山大和弗齐亚被球员拯救了，而出生于约克郡的市场交易员<strong>杰克被送回家</strong>。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Maia Gouveia（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg" alt="迈亚在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Maia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827331" class="wp-caption-text"> Maia在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在她的姐姐在最后一个圆桌会议上被驱逐出境之后，叛徒选择谋杀玛雅，以取出可能是强大的对手。她的去世还对弗雷迪（Freddie）引起了怀疑，弗雷迪（Freddie）以前在上一场圆桌会议上以她为目标。</p><p><strong>放逐：卡西姆·艾哈迈德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg" alt="叛徒的卡西姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827327" class="wp-caption-text"> Kasim被驱逐出每个人的沮丧：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>这是不幸的必然性，卡西姆被从小组中被驱逐出来，因为他只是太好了，而且 - 至少在杰克的脑海中 - 因为他是一名医生。阿玛尼（Armani）是在莫名其妙地为他保证他之后，在上一个圆桌会议上封锁了命运的人，其他球员说服他也是叛徒。</p><p><strong>放逐：泰勒·史密斯（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827710" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827710" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827710" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg" alt="泰勒叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Tyler-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827710" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管弗雷迪（Freddie）发热量，但当莱昂（Leon）和莱恩（Leanne）开始怀疑他们内心圈子中的某人时，潮汐在圆桌会议上与29岁的理发师泰勒（Tyler）脱颖而出。他的离开引起了利维（Livi）的特别激动的反应，利维（Livi）因决定而流泪。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Livi Deane（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828057" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828057" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828057" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg" alt="利维叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Livi-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828057" class="wp-caption-text"> Livi在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>为了将弗雷迪（Freddie）进一步加入射击线，叛徒决定杀死26岁的美容师和模特丽维（Livi）在圆桌会议上的情感爆发之后。</p><p><strong>放逐：丹·伯德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3828064" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828064" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828064" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg" alt="丹在叛徒中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Dan-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828064" class="wp-caption-text">丹在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管在剧集之前没有在任何人的雷达上，但丹在挑战期间的谎言还是在圆桌会议上撤消了他。 Leanne和Minah都面临着他的面对面，他们将焦点放在了他的隐藏真理上。</p><h2>谁在第三周离开？</h2><p>第三周的第一次谋杀案有一个转折。叛徒挑选了四名参赛者玩一场名为“死亡比赛”的纸牌游戏，其失败者将被谋杀。</p><p> Leon，Alexander，Fosia和Anna被选为比赛。每轮的获胜者都免于谋杀。</p><p>其余的球员在下一个任务中发现了比赛的结果，他们在棺材里找到了幸存的球员。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：Fozia Fasil（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="Fozia Fasil" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/fozia-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829330" class="wp-caption-text"> “叛徒”中的Fozia：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在对阵莱昂的指甲决赛中，弗齐亚是死亡比赛结束时最后一位站在死亡比赛结束的球员。然后，她被叛徒谋杀了。</p><p><strong>放逐：琳达·兰德斯（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829332" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829332" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829332" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg" alt="琳达" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/linda-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829332" class="wp-caption-text">琳达在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>经过几天的怀疑，包括在圆桌会议上进行了几次密切的电话，琳达成为了第二次从游戏中驱逐的叛徒。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：安娜·杜克（Anna Duke）（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829726" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829726" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829726" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg" alt="安娜·杜克（Anna Duke）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/anna-studio-lambert-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829726" class="wp-caption-text">安娜在“叛徒”信用中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在夏洛特被招募为叛徒之后，她和米纳（Minah）决定安娜在城堡的时间结束，她“不再需要”。在比赛中，安娜曾被怀疑是一名叛徒，在被选为死亡比赛之后，觉得叛徒出去了。叛徒以前曾试图招募她，但她拒绝了。</p><p><strong>放逐：Alex Oleksy（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3829736" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3829736" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3829736" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="叛徒的亚历克斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/alex-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3829736" class="wp-caption-text">亚历克斯在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>在整个比赛中，亚历克斯大部分都在雷达下飞行，但是厨房里的评论不佳证明了他的垮台。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：丽莎·库普兰（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831243" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831243" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831243" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg" alt="叛徒的丽莎·库普兰" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Lisa-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831243" class="wp-caption-text">丽莎在“叛徒”信用中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>叛徒认为她是一个无法撒谎的值得信赖的信徒，在经过一些尖锐的观察之后决定谋杀英国国教牧师丽莎。</p><p><strong>放逐：莱昂·杰克曼（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831242" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831242" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831242" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg" alt="莱昂叛徒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Leon-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831242" class="wp-caption-text">莱昂在“叛徒”中：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>忠实者在死亡比赛后的举止发生了变化后，对零售商店经理莱昂（Leon）感到怀疑，导致他最亲密的盟友反对他。</p><h2>谁在第四周离开？</h2><p>该节目的最后一周以相对直截了当的方式开始，残酷地谋杀和扭曲的国际象棋比赛。</p><p>仅剩两个圆桌会议，剩下的八名选手之间的紧张局势达到了历史最高的高度。然而，游戏将通过嘲笑的秘密力量将其脑海中的脑海。</p><p><strong>被谋杀：乔·斯科特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831230" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831230" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831230" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg" alt="乔·斯科特（Joe Scott）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/joe-the-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831230" class="wp-caption-text">乔在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>乔（Joe）是该小组的非常声音的成员，经常在圆桌会议上提出想法 - 无论他们是错误的。但是，这最终与他无能为力，因为叛徒认为谋杀他将传达强烈的信息。</p><p><strong>放逐：米纳·香农（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831236" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831236" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831236" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg" alt="米亚" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/minah-the-traitors-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831236" class="wp-caption-text">米亚在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>米纳（Minah）从一开始就以叛徒的身份发挥了一场强大的比赛，并避免了很长时间的怀疑，但最终，这一切都变得脱节了。最后，叛徒夏洛特（Charlotte）将她扔到公共汽车下，进行了最后一票，这意味着她被驱逐出城堡。</p><p>被淘汰后，最后一位剩下的叛徒夏洛特（Charlotte）选择招募弗雷迪（Freddie），他勉强接受了邀请。</p><p><strong>放逐：弗雷迪·弗雷泽（Freddie Fraser）（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3831608" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831608" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831608" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg" alt="弗雷迪·弗雷泽（Freddie Fraser）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/freddie-fraser-traitors-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831608" class="wp-caption-text">弗雷迪在“叛徒”中。学分：BBC/Studiolambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管夏洛特欺骗了新招募的叛徒弗雷迪谋杀Leanne，但在节目的倒数第二集中没有谋杀，尽管她没有盾牌，但她无法被谋杀。通过弗雷迪（Freddie）笨拙的撒谎尝试，他被忠实的洞察力，随后被驱逐出境。</p><p>在任务中获得最多的钱后，弗朗西斯卡（Francesca）获得了先知的力量，使她能够在一次私人会议上发现一名选手的真正身份。在一个戏剧性的悬崖峭壁中，我们发现她选择揭露夏洛特。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">本周在“叛徒”上被杀害的哨所？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
瑞士技术DJ和制片人Aldanya在癌症之后去世https://www.nme.com/news/music/swiss-techno-dj-and-producer-aldanya-dies-after-cancer-battle-3831601?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=swiss-techno-dj-and-生产者 -  aldanya-dies-ter-catter-cattle-battleLaura Molloy Thu, 23 Jan 2025 21:51:42 +0000 Music NewsNews..DanceElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3831601 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦技术场景的致敬一直在涌入</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/swiss-techno-dj-and-producer-aldanya-dies-after-cancer-battle-3831601">瑞士邮政技术DJ和制片人Aldanya在癌症战后去世，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="NME新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/NME-news-breaking-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>瑞士Techno DJ和制片人Aldanya（真名Crystal Margaret）在与癌症作斗争后死亡。</p><p>玛格丽特（Margaret）的家人证实，在与“侵略性形式的乳腺癌形式”作斗争后，她于周日（1月19日）去世。他们在对<a href="https://mixmag.net/read/swiss-techno-dj-aldanya-died-following-battle-cancer-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Mixmag的</em></a>一份声明中写道：“我们都伤心欲绝。”</p><p>他们继续说：“她是最善良，最慷慨，才华横溢，美丽的人，还有更多无数的品质。” “水晶留下了遗产，她受到了许多人的爱，只要我们活着，她就会在我们心中。”</p><p>玛格丽特（Margaret）首次接触音乐，始于在家，她在童年时期弹奏古典钢琴。在她十几岁的时候，她对舞蹈音乐产生了兴趣，并自学到DJ，然后在伦敦的Point Blank音乐学校学习。</p><p>玛格丽特（Margaret）开发了舞台名称Aldanya，以制作技术和室内音乐而闻名，在首都的著名场所中演奏，包括面料，Fold，Werkhaus，Willkhaus，乡村地下，热身节日和Steelyard。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Aldanya- Just Techno-与客人DJ -Riva -Riva-直播伦敦17-04-2022" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2ZA2rmAJCPE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Techno社区的致敬一直在社交媒体上涌入，折衷的动物​​园事件写作，他们“伤心欲绝”以听到这一消息。他们写道：“她会被人们铭记为每个人都在这里的人，一个正在照顾她的朋友并总是扩大新想法的人，如何改善音乐行业。” “她会很想念很多。”</p><p> “这是一场巨大的震惊和一场真正的悲剧，水晶是一个可爱的人，是一个非常有才华的DJ和制作人，” Khazad的负责人Balrog（英国唱片公司都发行了她的音乐）Balrog在给<em>Mixmag</em>的一份声明中说。 “她将对现场造成巨大损失。我的想法向她的朋友和家人发表。”</p><p>伦敦狂欢社区热身，也向玛格丽特（Margaret）表示敬意：“她对音乐的感染力在她的强大表演中总是很明显，这些表演吸引了许多心。她是一个真正美丽的人，散发着爱，温暖和善良。” DJ EBRA AL写道：“世界失去了您太早了。我爱你，你永远不会被遗忘。在音乐中休息，我美丽的朋友。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DFDxDOyMsPQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #